txt.en: 'Oh, I think I have celebrated too much!'
'I am a tad under the weather, my friends! But don't mind me!'
'Oh, the Spring Festival makes my head spin!'
'I ate too much, and I drank too much. But I love springtime!'
'Pay me no mind, my friends! I shall be better in a moment!'
'Three cheers for Spring! Three cheers for... oh, my head....'
'More wine! That is just what I need!'
'I feel dizzy... with happiness! No, this is just regular dizziness.'
'This happens to me every Spring Festival. Next time I will be better!'
